'''Davik's war suit''' was a [[Color/Legends|purple]] custom-built suit of medium [[Armor/Legends|armor]] worn by the [[Taris/Legends|Tarisian]] [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] and [[Exchange]] boss [[Davik Kang]]. Davik spared no expense when it came to his own personal safety and his personal armor provided ample protection against [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] fire and basic melee weapons. It was often underestimated by the odd [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] or [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] who engaged the crime boss in a confrontation that ended in the hapless opponent's [[Death/Legends|death]]. It proved, however, to be of little use when Davik faced off against [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] and his companions as the many [[Warship/Legends|warships]] of the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] blockade above Taris bombed the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] into submission. It afforded the wearer protection from extreme heat and cold, but hampered the [[The Force/Legends|Force]] abilities of any [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]] who wore it.

